Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:33.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）不破真広→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuwa Mahiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.27,0:01:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,could you kill Takigawa Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は　滝川吉野を殺せるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（不破真広）ふっ。　なんだよ　それ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not even a funny joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジョークにしても笑えねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:47.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好んで戯れ言を言う趣味はない。\Nくっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I rarely jest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）\Nまあ　おいおいと説明しよう。→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,着替えるといい。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:58.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ。\N（左門）安心しろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:00.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,傷は完治させた。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have healed your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I also healed any old injuries or broken bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:04.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついでに\N古傷や骨折痕も治してやったぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:07.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で　今日は　何月何日だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What's the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:10.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１月１日だ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,January 1st.
