Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(640,435)}Happy New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.94,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(640,435)}Happy New Year
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(675,510)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.94,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(675,510)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あけましておめでとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（滝川吉野）\N正月早々　お墓参りに行くのって→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be the only people who would visit a grave first thing on January 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:20.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕たちくらいかも。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:23.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）２年後か…。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\N私が迎える由のなかった正月だ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't even be around to celebrate this New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering that I was meant to be dead on that island two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来　２年前に　私は→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無人島で\N朽ちていたはずだったのだからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　そういうことになるのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）お前のおかげだ。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... you and Mahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや…　「真広とお前の」だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）はじまりの樹が\Nどう世界を変えたか→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess is traveling to various places
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to see for herself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:49.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを　自分の目で確かめるため→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,how the Tree of Genesis has changed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今　姫様は　あちこち回っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで　それに吉野が？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did Yoshino go with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姫様が同行を許したのが→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one the princess would allow to accompany her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,滝川吉野だけだったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,was Takigawa Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっ　随分と\N気に入られたもんじゃねぇか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like she's taken quite a liking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが　笑い事では済まぬ火種と\Nなりつつある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that is gradually becoming a serious situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）待ってたのよ～。→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっ　座って　座って。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しげなメンツだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What a merry gathering this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:21.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）\N私が命じぬかぎりは　静かな男だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man of restraint unless I order otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd better be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:25.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ。　こんなとこで\N槍を振り回されてたまるかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If he starts waving his damn spear around, it won't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:32.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）胃腸も弱っておらんはずだ。\N気にせず食べろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be fairly hungry. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつも　魔法のおかげか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is all this from magic, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　初対面だった？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you two haven't met yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't met me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:43.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）一方的にだが\N私は　君を目にしている。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If only on the monitor when he was heading to Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,富士に向かう途中で\N軍のモニター越しだったがね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa Takumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早河巧。　黒鉄病対策本部長補佐→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Assistant Director of the Black Iron Syndrome Countermeasures Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:56.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時点ではね。\N過去形かよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）あれだけの軍を動員し\N結果がどうなったか→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This disaster happened under my command after I mobilized a massive force.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君が\N意識を失う以前の状況だけでも→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you lost consciousness for part of it, I'm sure you can guess what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおむね　見当がつくはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's a bureaucrat in charge of assembling statistical reports on the Black Iron Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:10.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今じゃ　黒鉄病関連の\N統計資料作成係って閑職。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So at the moment, all he can do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使いのうわさを→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is spread online rumors about the mage of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:15.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ネットに流すくらいしか\Nできないってわけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The mage of Exodus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:18.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使い…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does one really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなのが　本当にいるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）それを\Nあぶり出すためにやっている。→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're spreading rumors to figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If one exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実在するとすれば\N新たな混乱を避けるため→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we want to find him first, before there is further chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:31.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いち早く捜し出し\Nこちらの管理下に置かねばならん。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to put him under our control.
