Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:39.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It's not fair of you to refuse text messages, Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:39.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村・心の声）≪メールまで拒否って\Nそりゃないよ　ゆっちゃん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あの樹が現れたとき\N大きな犠牲が払われたけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:49.51,Defalics,,0,0,0,,When the Tree appeared, there were lots of victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから\N確かに　世界は平和になった≫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:52.95,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But it's also true that the world became peaceful after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:57.35,Defalics,,0,0,0,,There are many who worship the Tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:57.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪樹のことを崇める人も\N少なくないけど…≫
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.33,0:05:06.20,Defalics,,0,0,0,,though every day, there are more and more rumors about a mage of Exodus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:06.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪でも　一方で\Nその樹を倒し　この世界を救う→
