Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:09.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹の魔法使いが\Nいるってうわさも→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:10.84,Defalics,,0,0,0,,who can defeat the Tree and restore the world to its previous state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日ごとに広まっている≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪なんとなく\Nみんな　感じてるんだ→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.26,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I think people are finally realizing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,that the Tree is ruling over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは\N樹に支配されてしまったって≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.35,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\blur0.8\c&H050605&\alpha&H70&\yshad1.2\fscx48\fscy83\4c&H606465&\4a&H80&\move(650,322,650,-5,31,3409)}Fuwa Family Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪愛花ちゃん→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.81,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Aika,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:27.52,Defalics,,0,0,0,,this began as a journey to find your killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君を殺した犯人を\N捜す旅だったのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:31.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今じゃ　とんでもなく\N大げさなことになってるよ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:31.22,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But it's become such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪世の中も\N随分　変わってしまって…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.20,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The world has changed quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:39.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野　不破愛花とは\Nどういう娘だったのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person was Fuwa Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと…　ほら→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she {\i1}is{\i0} Mahiro's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの真広の妹ですから…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:49.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たちが悪そうな娘ということか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As in, she was also a very difficult person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:52.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪かったですね。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:06:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花嬢の彼氏に\N私も一度　会わせてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please introduce me to Aika's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nあの真広の妹と→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To secretly date Mahiro's younger sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:06.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠れてつきあうとは\Nなんとも　命知らずなヤツだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that idiot must have no sense of self-preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔が見てみたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:12.05,Defalics,,0,0,0,,So I'm apparently an idiot with no sense of self-preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:12.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪僕が　その\N命知らずの彼氏なんですけどね≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:16.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不破愛花\Nまた改めて謝罪に参ろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuwa Aika, let me apologize once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:21.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事によると　お前を死なせたのは\N私かもしれん。→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that I caused your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　一体　どれだけの命を→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many lost lives I've been responsible for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犠牲にしてしまったのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪富士に現れたのが→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:39.18,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If it really was the Tree of Exodus that appeared at Mt. Fuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:39.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとに\N絶園の樹だっていうんなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:43.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Maybe if we could revive it fully, we'd be able to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全に復活させれば\N世界が元に戻るかも≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:49.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪僕がやれるのかな？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.73,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could actually do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪でも　それができたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.48,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:54.39,Defalics,,0,0,0,,maybe my girlfriend would come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女が\N戻ってきてくれるかもしれない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\Nこの街で暮らしていたのだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the city where you lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　まあ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this place holds many memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\N思い出すことは　いろいろあろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably more bad ones than good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思い出したくないことの方が\N多いかも。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪今の葉風さんは　おそらく→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.70,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Right now, I think Ms. Hakaze
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.66,Defalics,,0,0,0,,fears the power of the Tree of Genesis more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰よりも\Nはじまりの樹の力を恐れている≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪僕たちが倒れたあと\N絶園の樹を抑え→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:20.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,We were told that after we'd passed out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:24.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hakaze suppressed the Tree of Exodus and stopped the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:24.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の活動を止めたのも\N葉風さんだという≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your fault, Ms. Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さんのせいじゃありませんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could have predicted that this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:34.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなことになるなんて\N誰も予想できやしません。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not understand because you were asleep at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は　眠っていたから\N実感として分からぬであろうが→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it only took seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:43.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった７日だ。\N破壊の跡が僅かに残るだけで→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Only traces of the destruction remained,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:47.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１週間で\N世界の大半が　元に戻ったのだ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with most of the world returning to normal in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:51.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金属化した死体も　はじまりの樹が\N吸収して消え去り→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The metallicized bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,were all absorbed by the Tree of Genesis and vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hear that most social problems have pretty much disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,社会生活にも　ほとんど\N問題がなくなったと聞く。→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろ　そのことの方が恐ろしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, that frightens me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:02.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は\Nはじまりの樹の力を見誤っていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated the Tree of Genesis's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is what happened with only a portion of the Tree awake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:07.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ一部が目覚めただけで\Nこれだけのことが起きたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:09.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全覚醒すれば　どうなるか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what would have happened had it fully revived?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But because it was only partially revived,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中途半端に目覚めたせいで→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it's also possible that meant more victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変に\N犠牲が出たのかもしれませんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the more I see, the less I'm certain as to what is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:21.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　私は　見れば見るほど\N何が正しいか分からなくなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your home and your friends have all disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:24.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の故郷も　友人たちも→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして奪ってしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかにも　きっと…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And there must be many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここを離れましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:39.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お正月なんですから\Nおいしいものでも食べましょうよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's New Year's, let's go get something good to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風が吉野にほれた!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakaze has a crush on Yoshino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess does not seem to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）\Nそれが　どういう感情であるか→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらく\N姫様は気付いてないだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,her current feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how she seems, the princess was rather sheltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:53.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姫様は　あれで　箱入り娘なのだ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹に守られた姫宮。→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She was protected by the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:00.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ\Nあの富士山麓での窮地は→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So what she experienced at Mt. Fuji
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,may have been her first taste of hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:03.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姫様が初めて味わった\N逆境だったと言える。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're the one to blame for all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が　その状況に\N落とし込んだんだけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one who saved her was Takigawa Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:11.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこを救ったのが滝川吉野だ。\Nスルーかよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:16.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）姫様さえ絶望した状況に\N果敢に立ち向かい→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When even she despaired, he persevered and found a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見事　道を切り開いた彼は→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So to the princess, he is the first reliable man in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:23.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姫様にとって　初めての\N頼れる男だったと言える。→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれん方がおかしい。\Nだとしても→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't she fall for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, how does any of this lead to killing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:30.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっから　それが\N吉野を殺せって話になるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）吉野。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you the other reason I had you accompany me on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:36.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前にだけ　旅に出た\Nもう一つの目的を教えておく。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:39.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹を\N完全に復活させるには→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For the Tree of Exodus to fully revive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it must absorb the remaining fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残りの果実を\N吸収させねばならない。→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, we need to track them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:47.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その所在を確かめるためにも\N各地を回る必要があった。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:50.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さん…。\Nあっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hakaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万一のためだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:54.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）姫様は揺れておられる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess is uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パン　パン
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）己の力を恐れ→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She fears the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この先どうするべきか\N迷っておられる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and is unsure as to what she should do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:06.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野の意見で\Nこの先どうするか決めるとでも？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that Yoshino's opinion may be a deciding factor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大きく左右されような。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he could greatly sway her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If Takigawa Yoshino says
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,滝川吉野が　はじまりの樹を→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,she should revive the Tree of Genesis, she will probably do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:15.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚醒させるべきと言えば\Nそうされるだろうし→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,べきでないと言えば\Nそうされよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he says she shouldn't, she will probably agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっ。　ほれた弱みってやつか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she's a sucker for the guy she loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not what it means to have your heart stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心を奪われるとは\Nそういうことだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今や姫様は→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, the princess
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,滝川吉野を中心に\N物事を考えているのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,makes every decision with Takigawa Yoshino in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ～。　つまり…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of the world has somehow ended up in Yoshino's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:36.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界の命運は\N吉野が握っちまったってことか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:45.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）吉野　少し待っててくれ。\Nはい。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino, please wait for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫（羽村）ごめん。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっといいかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪なっておらん…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.57,Defalics,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:01.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪また　吉野の前で\N情けないところを見せてしまった≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:11:00.64,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I keep acting like a fool in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:04.91,Defalics,,0,0,0,,And he has no obligation to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:05.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そもそも　吉野が\N私に従う義理も　すでにない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:08.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪いまだ巻き込み　余計な\N負担ばかり　かけているのも→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:10.31,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I also have to face the fact that, even now, I'm involving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反省せねばならん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪いや　吉野も吉野だ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.92,Defalics,,0,0,0,,No, Yoshino is to blame, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.25,Defalics,,0,0,0,,He is too kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あやつは　人がよすぎる≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪断るべきところは断れ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.46,Defalics,,0,0,0,,He should refuse if he doesn't want to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.75,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そんなんだから\N私や真広などに振り回されて→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:22.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,he keeps letting Mahiro and me pull him into terrible situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひどい目にも遭うのだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.59,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, I hear that he has a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪聞けば　あやつ\N彼女もいるというではないか≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪私に付き従っている場合では\Nなかろう≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.33,Defalics,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't be following me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪振られても知らんぞ\Nうらなりめ！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.58,Defalics,,0,0,0,,He'd better not cry to me if he gets dumped... Cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪しかし　吉野ほどの男の彼女だ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.14,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.18,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Considering his own qualities,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪よくできた娘なのだろうな…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.61,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Yoshino's girlfriend must be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.07,Defalics,,0,0,0,,As if I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:44.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪私の知ったことか！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪（羽村）\Nあっ　行き方は分かりました。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to get there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも\N今は動いていないはずですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think that train runs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:55.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか…。\Nはい。　ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:57.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）えい！\N（羽村）ううっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だ？　あの男は。\Nえっ　誰って…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You kicked him without even knowing who he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:06.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らないのに蹴ったんですか？\Nなっ　なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:10.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何やら胸騒ぎがしてな。\Nまずかったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:13.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ～。\Nまあ　しかたありませんか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪しっ　しかたないんだ!?≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.19,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:20.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）で　誰なんだ？\N乗り換えを聞かれてただけですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just asking me about a transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,富士山に行くって。\N（葉風）はあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to go to Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様はバカか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:28.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの周辺は\N立ち入り禁止なのを知らんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know that area is off-limits?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪確かに…→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:33.44,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It's true that the Tree of Exodus remaining in the area
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:35.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの地に残った絶園の樹は\N異変の原因の一つと目され→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.08,Defalics,,0,0,0,,is believed to be partly responsible for the catastrophe,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許可された者以外\N接近は禁じられている≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.86,Defalics,,0,0,0,,so only authorized personnel can enter the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪もっとも　あの周囲には→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:45.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,And Ms. Hakaze put up basically permanent barrier around that Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:45.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さんが\N半永久的な結界を張ったのだから→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:48.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,各国から送り込まれた調査団も→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:50.89,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Even groups sent from other countries to \Nexamine the Tree have been unable to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:50.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹に\N接触できていないはずだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:59.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）立ち入り禁止なのは\N知っています。→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it's off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I sort of have to go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:02.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　行かないといけない\Nっていうか…。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの…　絶園の魔法使いの\Nうわさって知ってます？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the rumors about the mage of Exodus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ。\N知っているどころか→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only have we heard, we know who spread the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのうわさを流したヤツも\N知っているぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ!?　じゃあ　話は早いのかな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that may make things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:20.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく　僕が　その\N絶園の魔法使いみたいなんですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I think I am that mage of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You said your name is Hanemura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）羽村といったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Megumu. Hanemura Megumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）めぐむです。　羽村めぐむ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you realize you had this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:31.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつ　その力に気付いた？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:34.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１年くらい前です。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,About a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:38.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急に　体から\N変な力が出せるようになって→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was suddenly able to use a strange power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And after the Tree of Exodus appeared, the power grew stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:42.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　あの絶園の樹とかいうのが\N現れたころから→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:46.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと強く\Nはっきり使えるようになったんです。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was able to use it more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:49.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）≪１年くらい前…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.45,Defalics,,0,0,0,,About a year ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪左門が絶園の樹復活を\N本格化させたころか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:53.30,Defalics,,0,0,0,,That's when Samon began enacting his plan for the Tree of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）そこに\N絶園の魔法使いのうわさを知って→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I heard the rumors about the mage of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought my power must have been related.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:01.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　このための力だったんだ\Nって思ったんですけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:05.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うんですか？\N（葉風）違うと言えば信じるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe I was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I said that wasn't it, would you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）えっと…　困ります。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:11.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）困るな。　貴様の力は→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so uncertain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That power is enough to make this building disappear in under a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この店　丸ごと\N半瞬で消し去れるほどのものだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ!?　そっ　そんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:22.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）≪こやつ\N本当に自覚がないのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:21.61,Defalics,,0,0,0,,He really has no idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:25.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪自分が　世の理さえ\N砕く力を持っているのを≫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.56,Defalics,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know he has the power to surpass the logic of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）まあ\Nそう硬くならず　食べたらどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you needn't be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）あっ　はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ　何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）貴様　魔法使いは→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think your were the only mage in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分一人だけだと思うか？\N（羽村）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹側の魔法使いが\Nいるなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are mages who side with the Tree of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今　この世界を\N支配している樹の側の→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then there should be mages who side with the Tree that rules this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔法使いもいるはずだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが私だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:55.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う…　うそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ　魔法使い同士→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Shall we spar a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとつ　手合わせしてみんか？\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:07.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）幸い　滝川吉野は\N姫様の恋心に気付かず→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, Takigawa Yoshino doesn't realize the princess's feelings for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:10.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界の命運を握った自覚もない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and has no idea that he holds the fate of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　あの少年→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that young man has the tendency
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かしら信じることがあれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to sacrifice others when he believes in something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:18.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あらゆるものを犠牲にして\N突っ走りそうな怖さがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything were to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）何かあれば　彼は\N迷わず　姫様の背中を押すだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he wouldn't hesitate to give the princess a little push.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　そうなる前に→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying you want to kill Yoshino before that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野を殺して排除しようってのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're asking for your help to prevent that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:32.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうならぬよう\N協力を頼んでいる。→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:37.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長いつきあいだと聞いた。\Nはぁ～。　あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you've known him for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野の彼女は!?\Nそっちは無事なんだろうな!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Yoshino's girlfriend? She'd better be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう聞いている。\N関わらせたくないのか→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that she's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know who she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps because he wishes to avoid involving her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名前一つ　教えてくれんがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:53.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪好きな女が生きてんなら\N吉野も　むちゃはしねぇだろう≫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.15,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If his girlfriend is alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.08,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I doubt that Yoshino will do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪心配ねぇか≫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.16,Defalics,,0,0,0,,So no cause for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）\Nどうだ？　協力してくれるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Will you cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（回想）((僕の彼女のこと\N誰にも話さないでください))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:03.64,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell anyone about my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((知ってる人が増えると→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.73,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The more people who know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:09.29,Defalics,,0,0,0,,the higher the chance Mahiro will accidentally find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:09.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広の耳に　うっかり入る可能性も\N高くなります))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:13.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((この状況で知られると\Nいかにも面倒でしょう？))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:13.14,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If he learned about it now, it would confuse things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪確かに　今は誰も\N知らない方がいいかもしれない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:18.47,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I admit it may be for the best that no one knows yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:22.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ただ　そんな吉野君の心の内は→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:24.49,Defalics,,0,0,0,,but I wonder what Yoshino is really thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際　どうなっているんだろう？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:28.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野対策に手を貸すぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help with the Yoshino plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:32.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのかわり　あんたらは\N愛花を殺したヤツを見つける。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have to help me find Aika's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その取り引きでいいか？\Nああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that deal work for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:41.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった。　あんたらの\N思いどおりに動いてやるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you guys want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪吉野　恩に着ろよ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.42,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You owe me, Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.83,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll protect you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ついでに　お前を守ってやるよ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:51.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）\Nいつまで　不破真広に隠しておく？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you intend to keep the truth from Fuwa Mahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）いずれ　彼も気付くだろう→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll realize soon enough
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:58.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,滝川吉野が\N絶園の魔法使いである可能性に。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that Takigawa Yoshino may be the mage of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）羽村　少し離れろ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanemura, step back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その方が\Nお前も　魔法を使いやすかろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That should make it easier for you to use magic, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）あっ　はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it dangerous to just start sparring like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いきなり手合わせって\N危なくありませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:13.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あやつが\Nどれほどの力と知識を持つか→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is I won't know how powerful he is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:17.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局　魔法を使わせてみなければ\N分からんのも事実だ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,unless I have him actually use his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't know whether he can kill or not, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:20.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに　人を殺せるかどうかもな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,案ずるな。　はじまりの姫宮が\N負けるようなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Princess of Genesis were to lose to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世で\Nあやつに勝てる者はいないぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,then no one could stand against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\Nルールは簡単だ。　魔法を使って→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your magic to get me to, at least, kneel on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の片膝でも\N地面に着けさせろ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it is your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば　貴様の勝ちだ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win, I will tell you everything you want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:41.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば　貴様の知りたいこと\Nすべて教えてやろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:45.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）えっと…　じゃあ\Nどうなれば　僕の負けでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, then how will I know if I lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:48.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の腕のどちらかが\N逆方向に曲がったらだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If either one of your arms bends in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ!?\N行くぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:54.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,樹の中の樹　大樹の中の大樹→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:52.69,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Tree within the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.41,Defalics,,0,0,0,,great tree within the great tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が名において聞き届けよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:56.35,Defalics,,0,0,0,,hear my words, and grant my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:08.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ　何？　うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）私ほどになれば\N防御フィールドを自在に変化させ→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At my level, I can manipulate the defensive barrier as I please,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:15.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠距離の相手を倒すことも可能だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and defeat opponents across great distances, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪こっ　これも魔法!?≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.92,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Magic can do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:24.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）≪羽村　貴様が本物なら→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.77,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Hanemura, if you are truly a mage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:27.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これくらいの魔法\Nたやすく破壊できるぞ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:27.18,Defalics,,0,0,0,,you can neutralize this magic with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪貴様に私を殺し→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.85,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Do you have the power to kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世の理を\N変える力はあるのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.65,Defalics,,0,0,0,,and change the logic of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:36.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）\N滝川吉野という少年の存在は→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Takigawa Yoshino's existence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の理から→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is starting to separate itself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:41.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ことごとく\N外れた結果をもたらしている。→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,from the logic of the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:46.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼が富士にいなくても\N姫様は　現代に戻りえたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even had he not been at Mt. Fuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the princess would have been able to return to this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？\N鎖部一族の中に→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We were unable to find the killer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不破真広の妹を殺した犯人は\N見つけられなかった。→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of Fuwa Mahiro's sister within the Kusaribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時点で　姫様は→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使い犯人説を\N導き出せたのだ→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the princess was able to theorize that the killer was the mage of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:02.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,滝川吉野が\Nいようが　いまいがな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether Takigawa Yoshino was there or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:06.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなれば　不破真広は\N再度　姫様と手を組み→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuwa Mahiro would have rejoined the princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:10.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,独力で　時間の檻を\N破る方法を見つけるか→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and would have discovered how to destroy the prison of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは\N魔具を発動させるかして→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or he would have activated the talisman,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姫様を戻す選択をしただろう。→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and figured out how to retrieve her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹は\Nあの少年を必要としなかった。→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Genesis had no need of the other young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に　あの少年によって→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was actually because of him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹に\N不利な現状がもたらされたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Tree of Genesis faced some inconsistencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？　ほう→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく\N魔法を使えるのを思い出したか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you finally remember that you can also use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:37.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そうだ　魔法だ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.63,Defalics,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.42,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪僕は　魔法が使える≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あの人は\N確かめようとしてるんだ→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.88,Defalics,,0,0,0,,She's testing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:45.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕に世界を救う力があるか→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.65,Defalics,,0,0,0,,To see if I have the power to change the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:48.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この先　戦う覚悟があるか≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.05,Defalics,,0,0,0,,and if I'll be able to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:50.60,Defalics,,0,0,0,,She probably isn't my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あの人は　たぶん敵じゃない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪やれる気がしてきた≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.95,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel like I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪僕の遺伝子に\N組み込まれていたものが→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:20:00.35,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I feel like something is awakening inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次々と目覚めているような…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行きます！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて　どこまで来れる？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's see how far you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）くっ！\Nドォーーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう　それは通じません！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,斬り裂け！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パキーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:26.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…　葉風さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hakaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ　腕が…　腕が！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your... Your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:36.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしよう!?\N（葉風）うろたえるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think I couldn't regrow a limb?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:40.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この私が\N腕一本　再生できんと思うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肉が散ったくらいで取り乱すな→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop sniveling over a little bit of flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,軟弱者！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:54.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\Nん？　本当に　逆に曲がったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His arm really did bend the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:56.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脅かさないでくださいよ\N葉風さん。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that, Ms. Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまんな。　砕けると同時に→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast a regeneration spell on my arm earlier that would activate upon serious damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再生する魔法を\Nかけておいたのだ→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:05.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あやつの反応を見るためにな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to judge his reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:09.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力は　確かに絶園のものだ。　だが→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,His power is indeed that of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But he isn't able to kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こやつに人は殺せんな。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:15.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）あらゆるものを\N破壊して揺るがぬ絶園の心を→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this boy has the heart of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:18.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この者が持つとは思えない。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the ability to destroy without mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:23.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）滝川吉野は\Nあえて　状況を複雑にし→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Takigawa Yoshino
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,has complicated the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and has somehow made the princess
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:27.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それらが　なぜか\N解決される異常性を突きつけ→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹への不信感を\N姫様に抱かせた。→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,begin to doubt the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:34.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして…。\Nその心まで奪っていった。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He stole her heart while he was at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の物語を狂わせ→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anyone who could disrupt the story of the Tree of Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その理を曲げた\Nイレギュラーな存在など→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使い以外\Nまず考えられん。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,besides the mage of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:48.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）\N彼が　絶園の魔法使いだとすると→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is the mage of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見事な仕事をしていることになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then he's quite competent at his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:54.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔法を使わずして\Nはじまりの樹の理をゆがめ→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Without using magic, he has disrupted the Tree of Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:58.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その命運を　ほぼ握ってみせた。\Nああ。　だが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and holds its fate in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:06.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪だが　彼が絶園の魔法使いなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:06.28,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But if he is the mage of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:11.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不破真広の妹を殺したのも\N滝川吉野となる≫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:11.11,Defalics,,0,0,0,,that would also make him the one who killed Fuwa Mahiro's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:13.71,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Can I even convince myself of that possibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:14.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そこまで言い切れるか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:16.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）ちょっといい!?\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:20.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野君から\N絶園の魔法使いが見つかったけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He says they found the mage of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and he wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:23.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちに　よこしていいかって…。
